### REST API Examples
# You can use these with tools like curl or HTTPie

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

### Get single product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category_id=1

### Get product reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1/reviews

### Get product inventory
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1/inventory

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories

### Get products in category
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/1/products

### Create product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "description": "A test product",
  "price": 99.99,
  "category_id": 1,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/test.jpg"
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "price": 149.99
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/1

### Create review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great product!",
  "author": "John Doe"
}
